item.title: US Stocks Picked
item.description: RKLB (Rocket Lab USA, Inc.) Small Despite net loss increase, Rocket Lab demonstrates strong performance in expanding its space systems capabilities and delivering on complex space missions, supported by confidence from investors and regulatory approvals. ZM (Zoom Video Communications, Inc.) Middle Zoom Video Communications Inc (NASDAQ: ZM) has shown impressive Q4 results with revenue exceeding estimates, but it faces potential challenges in the form of competition and a slowdown in demand.
